data.description: REDUCED $5,000! One of the most spacious condos in the North Center area!!! 2 bedroom, 2 bath loft condo that has a living room with cozy fireplace, updated kitchen with stainless steel appliances, California closets in the master bedroom. Master bath with Jacuzzi tub, and an in-unit laundry. Parking included, with 1 car heated garage. There's also a storage unit. Huge balcony with wood decking. Pet friendly building. Close access to shopping, dining, public transportation, and highways.
